1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 9=

3
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,480
Ke'er, where have you been?

4
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,280
None of your business.

5
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,840
Countrywomen love wandering.

6
00:01:07,959 --> 00:01:08,719
Don't you know that?

7
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,239
Well,

8
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:11,480
thanks to you,

9
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,799
I'm covered in bruises.

10
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:14,040
Will you take care of me?

11
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:15,519
Out of nowhere,

12
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,480
as a fragile military physician
who can't even care for yourself,

13
00:01:17,599 --> 00:01:18,400
and you don't even set foot
on the battlefield,

14
00:01:18,519 --> 00:01:19,680
how did you even get hurt?

15
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,519
I'm telling the truth. See for yourself.

16
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:23,239
I haven't healed from last time.

17
00:01:27,599 --> 00:01:28,359
It doesn't hurt.

18
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:31,120
Aren't you a physician?

19
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,519
Treat yourself. Bye.

20
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,319
Even physicians have their limits.

21
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,079
I can't even tend to my own wounds
right now.

22
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:42,000
Please, heroic lady, take care of me.

23
00:01:42,159 --> 00:01:43,239
Keep being nice, will you?

24
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,000
If you get handsy with me again,

25
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:46,879
you're dead.

26
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:49,040
You're being too dramatic.

27
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:51,200
You're a grown man. Don't freak out.

28
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:53,239
I get hurt all the time, and I'm fine.

29
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:56,280
All the time?

30
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:58,400
Have you been on the battlefield?

31
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,519
Life itself is a battlefield.

32
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,480
Whether you're hauling water,

33
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:06,719
doing laundry, or taking care of kids,

34
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,199
everything is like a war.

35
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,120
Now...

36
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:09,919
Enough.

37
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:13,439
Actually,

38
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,680
I can do these for you.

39
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:22,840
It's getting late.

40
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:24,319
Go make dinner.

41
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,319
I have other things to do.

42
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:26,960
Well, you...

43
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,599
I will find a way to cure Liuli.

44
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:38,280
Your Majesty.

45
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:42,240
You are especially devoted
to Miss Liuli.

46
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,560
Nine-section Sweet Flag?

47
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:46,879
(Nine-section Sweet Flag)

48
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,479
(Nine-section Sweet Flag)
I've never seen you so devoted before.

49
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:51,360
(Nine-section Sweet Flag)
Though she has a gentle temperament,

50
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,240
I can feel

51
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,240
that she is unlike
the other women in the palace.

52
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,639
I wonder what it is she truly seeks.

53
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,800
If they are the same person,

54
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:01,400
how could temperament

55
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,000
and appearance

56
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,120
be changed in so little time?

57
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:07,719
If she is pretending,

58
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:11,159
then why do I sense
some sincerity in her?

59
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,400
Sheng,

60
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,039
no matter what it takes,

61
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:17,520
find this herb

62
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:18,639
and cure her.

63
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:19,759
Yes, Your Majesty.

64
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:24,120
Your Majesty, there is one more thing.

65
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,479
Miss Zhao has been on her knees outside,

66
00:03:26,879 --> 00:03:27,879
begging for your forgiveness.

67
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:28,560
I won't see her.

68
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,360
After all, Miss Zhao is
the Prime Minister's daughter.

69
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:34,680
You owe your throne
to the Prime Minister's faction.

70
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,199
Are you really not going to see her?

71
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,400
Prime Minister Zhao is cunning.

72
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,680
If it were someone else

73
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:41,759
sitting on this throne,

74
00:03:42,479 --> 00:03:44,039
they would switch sides just the same.

75
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,319
I need to find a way to control them.

76
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,199
I can't let one faction dominate.

77
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:52,159
Not a word they say can be trusted.

78
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,520
Yes, Your Majesty.

79
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,520
Miss Zhao, you may leave.

80
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,240
Do you know who I am?

81
00:04:05,719 --> 00:04:07,560
I am the Prime Minister's only daughter!

82
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,680
Let me in!

83
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:10,800
Miss Zhao,

84
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:12,439
His Majesty is feeling unwell today.

85
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:13,759
Please come another day.

86
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,599
What's wrong with His Majesty?

87
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:16,319
Is he under the weather?

88
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:17,839
Let me see him.

89
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:18,839
Miss Zhao,

90
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:20,560
His Majesty is not seeing anyone today.

91
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:21,560
Please take your leave.

92
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,079
By His Majesty's command,

93
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:26,680
no entry without permission.

94
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,800
Violators beware.

95
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,759
(Honored ancestors,)

96
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:38,519
(Ancestral Tablets of the Mu clan)
(Father,)

97
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,160
(Ancestral Tablets of the Mu clan)
Ruyi is back.

98
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,600
(Ling Xiao,)

99
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,959
(your name will be on the tablet soon.)

100
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,600
My Lady,

101
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:52,879
what are you doing here?

102
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,399
I've been searching everywhere for you.

103
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,839
Whose spirit hall is this?

104
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:03,879
This is just a side palace.

105
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:05,519
I'm afraid I can't answer that.

106
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,600
I wonder

107
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,800
when I'll recover.

108
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,800
My Lady, don't be anxious.

109
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,279
Take your time,

110
00:05:13,439 --> 00:05:14,680
and you will heal eventually.

111
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:18,360
His Majesty found
the Nine-section Sweet Flag for you,

112
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:20,040
which is extremely rare and precious.

113
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:22,519
He ordered the Imperial Hospital
to make it into a medicinal brew.

114
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:23,920
Please drink it while it's warm.

115
00:05:24,439 --> 00:05:26,360
It will help you recover.

116
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:30,680
No wonder

117
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,560
he's missing these days.

118
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,360
His Majesty went through great trouble

119
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,519
to obtain this herb.

120
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,759
He also has state affairs to attend to.

121
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,399
So he truly can't get away.

122
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:44,000
That's why he sent me
to deliver the brew instead.

123
00:05:44,439 --> 00:05:45,160
Thank you.

124
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:51,279
What terrible luck.

125
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,600
The one I want to see, I can't see him.

126
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,600
The one I don't want to see,
she's everywhere.

127
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:58,439
What are you doing here?

128
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,000
You can barely walk,
and yet you're everywhere.

129
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,000
Why?

130
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,600
Feeling threatened by me now?

131
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,879
Trying to act fragile

132
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,240
to win Ling Xiao's sympathy?

133
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,360
You siren!

134
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,360
You don't own this place.

135
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,240
I come and go as I please.

136
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:21,199
What I do is none of your business.

137
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:23,240
Look at you, pale and weak.

138
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,560
Ling Xiao would never grace

139
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,120
a wretch who can't please him.

140
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,560
Our Zhao clan

141
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,839
can keep Ling Xiao securely
on the throne.

142
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,079
To Ling Xiao,

143
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:34,519
you're just a plaything.

144
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:36,600
Get lost, unless you want trouble.

145
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,920
His Majesty brought me here,

146
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:41,000
so I'm not leaving.

147
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:45,800
Your Majesty!

148
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,839
I was trying to chat with her,

149
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:49,879
but she threw insults at me.

150
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:51,399
I lost my temper for a moment, so I...

151
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:54,000
I didn't mean it.

152
00:07:01,519 --> 00:07:02,639
From this day forth,

153
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,920
Jing Liuli shall be titled Consort Li.

154
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,959
She shall hold an honored position
in the palace.

155
00:07:07,959 --> 00:07:09,839
Everyone shall treat her
with utmost respect.

156
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:11,480
She must be shown proper respect.

157
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:12,639
Yes.

158
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,519
As for you, Zhao Sisi.

159
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:20,759
You are brutal,
and you abuse your power.

160
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:23,519
You shall be imprisoned
in the dungeon and punished.

161
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,199
You shall never leave
without permission.

162
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:25,879
Yes.

163
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:28,120
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

164
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:30,079
Your Majesty,
you can't treat me like this!

165
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:31,519
You will regret this!

166
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:35,560
Your Majesty,

167
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,319
I'm only a court singer
from a music house,

168
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:40,560
while she is
the Prime Minister's only daughter.

169
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:43,279
If you offend her for my sake,

170
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,879
what is to become in the future?

171
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,160
Your status

172
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,160
doesn't change who you are.

173
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,879
My word alone

174
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,279
makes you worthy.

175
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:07,759
Your Majesty.

176
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:12,920
Why haven't you taken the brew today?

177
00:08:14,759 --> 00:08:15,759
I'll take it later.

178
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,279
Is there something bothering you?

179
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:23,800
Your Majesty.

180
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:27,040
It looks like
the Ruyi Palace was recently renovated.

181
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,920
It's quite exquisite.

182
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,000
But looking at the furnishings,

183
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:34,080
someone might have lived here.

184
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,399
May I ask which noble lady

185
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:38,559
once resided here?

186
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,480
They're just old things.

187
00:08:43,639 --> 00:08:44,320
Just ignore them.

188
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:47,440
Could Your Majesty be hiding something?

189
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:53,480
Could it have something to do
with Mu Ruyi,

190
00:08:53,759 --> 00:08:56,279
the person you mistook me for
when we first met?

191
00:08:58,679 --> 00:08:59,320
Your Majesty.

192
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:03,200
Do I bear a striking resemblance to her?

193
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:06,240
Is that why you treat me this way?

194
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,200
Say no more of this.

195
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:13,679
Your Majesty.

196
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,200
Consort Li.

197
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,919
His Majesty treats you so well.

198
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,600
Why did you say something so hurtful

199
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:22,799
and upset him?

200
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:24,519
You've been in the palace
for a long time.

201
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,360
Can you tell me everything

202
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:28,679
about the Princess and His Majesty?

203
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,799
All of them.

204
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:32,519
Why trouble yourself with old stories,

205
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,639
Consort Li?

206
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,480
His Majesty treats me with sincerity,

207
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,799
and I truly love him in return.

208
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:41,039
I don't want to be
a substitute for anyone.
